Evocation [Fire]
Level: Sor/Wiz 2
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: Close (25 ft. + 5 ft/2 levels)
Area: 5 ft wide path to close range
Duration: Instantaneous
Saving Throw: Reflex Half
Spell Resistance: Yes

A jet of roaring flame bursts from your outstretched hand, scorching any creature in a 5' wide path to the edge of the spells range.  The spell deals 1d8 points of damage per two caster levels, to a maximum of 5d8 points of damage.